  <summary date="2020-02-13T21:09:24Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Ravi Thackurdeen Safe Students Study Abroad Act

This bill (1) applies campus-security reporting requirements to study-abroad programs of&#160;institutions of higher education that participate in federal student-aid programs, and (2) requires such institutions to implement&#160;specified policies&#160;to protect students participating in study-abroad programs.</summary>
